</blockquote>
<ul>
<li><p><strong>示例</strong></p>
  <figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">github_banner:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br><span class="line">  permalink: https://github.com/lyfdnrjbrs</span><br><span class="line">  title: Follow me on GitHub</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
<li><p><strong>效果图</strong></p>
  <img src="/images/xgt-banner.png" style="margin: 0;">
  <br></li>
</ul>
<h3 id="字体自定义设置"><a href="#字体自定义设置" class="headerlink" title="字体自定义设置"></a>字体自定义设置</h3><p>打开站点配置文件，找到 <code>font</code>，按照以下说明修改并保存：</p>
<blockquote>
<p><code>global: </code> 设置全局字体，整个网站使用的字体。<br><code>title: </code> 设置标题字体，站点标题使用的字体。<br><code>headings</code>  设置标题字体，文章标题使用的字体（h1、h2、h3、h4、h5、h6）。<br><code>pposts : </code>设置文章字体，文章使用的字体。<br><code>codes: </code>设置代码字体，文章中代码块使用的字体。</p>
</blockquote>
<ul>
<li><p><strong>示例</strong></p>
  <figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">font:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br><span class="line">  host:</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  # Global font settings used for all elements inside &lt;body&gt;.</span><br><span class="line">  global:</span><br><span class="line">    external: true</span><br><span class="line">    family: Monda</span><br><span class="line">    size: 1.125</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  # Font settings for site title (.site-title).</span><br><span class="line">  title:</span><br><span class="line">    external: true</span><br><span class="line">    family: Lobster Two</span><br><span class="line">    size:</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  # Font settings for headlines (&lt;h1&gt; to &lt;h6&gt;).</span><br><span class="line">  headings:</span><br><span class="line">    external: true</span><br><span class="line">    family: Amita</span><br><span class="line">    size:</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  # Font settings for posts (.post-body).</span><br><span class="line">  posts:</span><br><span class="line">    external: true</span><br><span class="line">    family: Montserrat</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  # Font settings for &lt;code&gt; and code blocks.</span><br><span class="line">  codes:</span><br><span class="line">    external: true</span><br><span class="line">    family: PT Mono</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
<li><p><strong>效果图</strong></p>
  <img src="/images/xgt-font.png" style="margin: 0;">
  <br></li>
</ul>
<h3 id="本地搜索设置"><a href="#本地搜索设置" class="headerlink" title="本地搜索设置"></a>本地搜索设置</h3><p>打开站点配置文件，找到 <code># Local Search</code>，按照以下说明修改并保存：</p>
<blockquote>
<p><code>enable: </code> 设置是否启用本地搜索功能，默认 <code>false</code> 是不启用，<code>true</code> 是启用</p>
<blockquote>
<p>注意：要提前在站点根目录执行以下命令进行安装：<br>    <strong>示例</strong><br>    <figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-generator-searchdb</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
</blockquote>
</blockquote>
<ul>
<li><p><strong>示例</strong></p>
  <figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">local_search:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true </span><br><span class="line">  trigger: auto</span><br><span class="line">  top_n_per_article: 1</span><br><span class="line">  unescape: false</span><br><span class="line">  preload: false</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
<li><p><strong>效果图</strong></p>
  <img src="/images/xgt-search1.png" style="margin: 0;">
  <br>
  <img src="/images/xgt-search2.png" style="margin: 0;">
  <br></li>
</ul>
